-- SC-IGNITE-007: Image staleness triggers rebuild at > maxImageAgeHours → rule GeneticResynthesis
-- SC-IGNITE-008: sil6Genome covers all 16 containers → invariant GenomeComplete

-- ─── SC-BOOT (Boot Sequence) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
