-- SC-BOOT-011: 7-level RCA on failure → rule SevenLevelAnalysis
-- SC-BOOT-012: RCA report generated → entity RcaReport

-- ─── SC-SIL4 (IEC 61508 Safety) ────────────────────────────────────────────
