--   → rule PreflightCheck ensures schema exists
-- AOR-IGNITE-004: ALWAYS record build results to BuildHistory
--   → rule GeneticResynthesis ensures BuildHistory.created(...)
-- AOR-IGNITE-005: Tier boot failures MUST halt pipeline
--   → rule TierBoot requires previous tiers healthy

