-- AOR-OODA-001: Observe budget ≤ 30ms → rule OodaObserve @guidance
-- AOR-OODA-002: Orient budget ≤ 20ms → rule OodaOrient @guidance
-- AOR-OODA-003: Decide budget ≤ 20ms → rule OodaDecideViaRules @guidance
-- AOR-OODA-004: Act budget ≤ 20ms → rule OodaAct @guidance
-- AOR-OODA-005: Total cycle ≤ 100ms → invariant OodaCycleSLA

-- ─── AOR-FUNC (Functional Invariant) ────────────────────────────────────────
-- AOR-FUNC-001: Verify compilation before commit → deferred (CI/CD)
-- AOR-FUNC-002: Checkpoint git state before risky ops → apoptosis checkpoint analogy
-- AOR-FUNC-005: Rollback on functional degradation → rule ApoptosisInitiate
-- AOR-FUNC-008: Halt if functional invariant violated → Jidoka principle

-- ─── AOR-TPS (Toyota Production System / Jidoka) ────────────────────────────
-- AOR-TPS-001: Stop on defect detection → rule EmergencyStop, rule GrlApoptosisCascade
-- AOR-TPS-002: Signal via Zenoh control plane → surface ZenohMeshBus.ApoptosisTriggered
-- AOR-TPS-003: 5-level RCA → rule SevenLevelAnalysis (7 levels, exceeds TPS)

-- ─── AOR-ZENOH (Zenoh Telemetry) ────────────────────────────────────────────
