-- AOR-ZENOH-007: Publish node health every 10s → surface ZenohMeshBus
-- AOR-ZENOH-008: Subscribe to cluster coordination on startup → external entity ZenohRouter

-- ─── AOR-DELETE (Deletion Safeguard) ────────────────────────────────────────
-- AOR-DELETE-001: Backup before deletion → DyingGaspCheckpoint pattern (analogous)
-- AOR-DELETE-002: Present deletion list before executing → surface OperatorDashboard exposes

-- =============================================================================
-- FMEA (Failure Mode and Effects Analysis)
-- =============================================================================
-- 15 failure modes with RPN scoring. Each maps to a GRL rule + recovery playbook.
-- RPN = Severity × Occurrence × Detection (scale 1-10 each, max 1000)

-- ─── FMEA Failure Mode Registry ─────────────────────────────────────────────
--
-- | # | Failure Mode                  | S | O | D | RPN | GRL Rule              | Recovery Playbook     |
-- |---|-------------------------------|---|---|---|-----|-----------------------|-----------------------|
-- | 1 | NIF Compilation Failure       | 9 | 4 | 7 | 252 | (preflight blocks)    | rebuild NIF deps      |
-- | 2 | Glibc/Musl Conflict           | 9 | 5 | 5 | 225 | (substrate_guard)     | rm _build/deps        |
-- | 3 | Fixed Health Timeouts         | 7 | 4 | 7 | 196 | GrlRestartOnDrift     | increase timeout      |
-- | 4 | Boot Ordering Race            | 8 | 3 | 7 | 168 | (DAG enforces order)  | retry with backoff    |
-- | 5 | Observability Gap             | 7 | 4 | 5 | 140 | (preflight PF-6)      | restart obs container |
-- | 6 | Cascading Failure             | 9 | 3 | 8 | 216 | GrlApoptosisCascade   | tier isolation        |
-- | 7 | Disk Exhaustion               | 8 | 3 | 7 | 168 | (external monitoring) | prune volumes/logs    |
-- | 8 | Memory Leak                   | 7 | 4 | 7 | 196 | GrlDrainMemoryLeak    | drain + restart       |
-- | 9 | Network Partition             | 9 | 2 | 7 | 126 | (partition.rs fences) | fence minority        |
-- |10 | Image Corruption              | 7 | 2 | 8 | 112 | GrlRebuildCorruptImage| rebuild image         |
-- |11 | Certificate Expiry            | 6 | 3 | 9 | 162 | GrlCertRotation       | rotate certs          |
-- |12 | Clock Drift                   | 5 | 4 | 8 | 160 | GrlNtpSync            | NTP resync            |
-- |13 | Zombie Process                | 5 | 4 | 7 | 140 | GrlZombieReap         | kill -9 + restart     |
-- |14 | Registry Unavailable          | 6 | 3 | 8 | 144 | GrlRegistryFailover   | use cached image      |
-- |15 | Configuration Drift           | 5 | 4 | 7 | 140 | GrlConfigReconcile    | config bridge sync    |
--
-- FMEA Invariants (SC-FMEA-001..008):
-- SC-FMEA-001: FMEA runs on every --analysis invocation
-- SC-FMEA-002: RPN = S × O × D formula
-- SC-FMEA-003: Severity: P0=9, P1=7, P2=5, P3=3
-- SC-FMEA-004: RPN >= 200 requires immediate action → GRL rules 1,2,6,8 address these
-- SC-FMEA-005: Results cached for retrieval
-- SC-FMEA-006: Top 15 entries persisted
-- SC-FMEA-007: Mitigation plan for RPN >= 100 → all 15 have playbooks
-- SC-FMEA-008: Trend tracked in sync history

